OL,3,C'Have an argument and get it out the
OL,4,Cway' - the secret of a 60+ year union
OL,6,FJennie Henry went to find out the
OL,7,Fsecret to a long and happy marriage
OL,9,FHaving an argument is fine - but
OL,10,Fgetting it out the way and moving on
OL,11,Fis what has kept one Teesside husband
OL,12,Fand wife together for 62 years.
OL,14,FEric and Letitia 'Letty' Blake met as
OL,15,Fteenagers and tied the knot at 20.
OL,17,FNow, more than six decades on, they
OL,18,Fstill only have eyes for each other.
