OL,3,C'Have an argument and get it out the
OL,4,Cway' - the secret of a 60+ year union
OL,6,F"I love her so much, she has no idea,"
OL,7,Fsaid Eric. "Even after 64 years. I'm
OL,8,Fgetting a lump in my throat again now.
OL,9,FI just wish everybody could have a
OL,10,Fmarriage like mine."
OL,12,FThe Blakes were one of three couples
OL,13,Fto be thrown a surprise party on
OL,14,FValentine's Day at their Eston care
OL,15,Fhome.
OL,17,FFellow Astune Rise residents, Anne and
OL,18,FNorman Bailes and Alan and Dorothy
OL,19,FHumphreys were also the guests of
OL,20,Fhonour.
