OL,3,C'Have an argument and get it out the
OL,4,Cway' - the secret of a 60+ year union
OL,6,FAll in their 80s and 90s, the three
OL,7,Fpairs of lovebirds have an impressive
OL,8,Fcombined 186 years of marriage.
OL,10,FThe Blakes married on 6 May 1961, the
OL,11,FBailes wed on 15 October 1964, but
OL,12,Fmarried for the longest are the
OL,13,FHumphreys who celebrate their 66th
OL,14,Fanniversary on 1 March.
OL,16,FAlan and Dorothy met at work - him
OL,17,F"upstairs in the office" and Dorothy
OL,18,F"downstairs typing".
