OL,3,C'Have an argument and get it out the
OL,4,Cway' - the secret of a 60+ year union
OL,6,FReflecting on their marriage, Dorothy
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've been together 62 years
OL,8,Fand I've had a wonderful, wonderful
OL,9,Flife."
OL,11,FFor care home manager Caroline
OL,12,FBowstead it only seemed right that
OL,13,Fthese couples' achievements should be
OL,14,Frecognised on Valentine's Day.
OL,16,FThe celebration itself was a combined
OL,17,Feffort, made possible via social media
OL,18,Fand by their local community who
OL,19,Fdonated decorations and cakes.
