OL,3,C'Have an argument and get it out the
OL,4,Cway' - the secret of a 60+ year union
OL,6,F"I think it's so special that today
OL,7,F(Wednesday) we're able to show them
OL,8,Fhow important their marriage is, you
OL,9,Fknow, their worth within the community
OL,10,Freally," said Caroline.
OL,12,FShe added: "Everybody, I think,
OL,13,Frecognises that we've got these
OL,14,Famazing couples living in a small care
OL,15,Fhome in Eston."
OL,17,FAfter a lifetime of marriage, Eric was
OL,18,Fhappy to pass on some advice for a
OL,19,Fsuccessful union.
