OL,3,C'Have an argument and get it out the
OL,4,Cway' - the secret of a 60+ year union
OL,6,F"That's the secret of a long marriage
OL,7,F- having an argument and getting it
OL,8,Fout of the way," he said.
OL,10,FOn the same page was wife Letty, who
OL,11,Fagreed, adding: "Put that argument at
OL,12,Frest before you might face another
OL,13,Fday."
